STATUS codes:\
1xx to 5xx (100 to 500)\
1xx -> informational codes\
2xx -> Success codes\
example: 200 OK, 201 Created, 204 No Content\
3xx -> redirection codes\
example: 302 Found, 307 Temporary Redirect\
4xx -> client error\
example: 401 Unauthorised, 403 Forbidden, 404 Not Found, 415 Unsupported Media Type\
5xx -> Server Error\
example: 500 Internal Server Error, \
